                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"indent(11)\"><placeName>The Hague</placeName>, <date>24 Dec.57</date>.</p>\n            <p>The Reverend</p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>I. Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear Sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">As soon as I did receive your kind letter (date<lb/>\n                <date>10 Nov.</date> last) I inform myself by several persons<lb/> and especially by\n                the Port. Charham here, the <persName>Rev. Ferares</persName>,<lb/> about the two\n                Sepharim, you are in need of. All<lb/> informations concur in two points, viz 1d\n                there no<lb/> being copies of the S. F. to be had here this moment,<lb/> and 2d. the\n                ordinary price being higher than you<lb/> fixed it. That price was ordinary to four\n                hundred<lb/> guilders (Neth. Money). The <persName>Rev. Ferares</persName> has\n                assu<lb/>red me, if you could for that price per copy<lb/> and <add>?</add> him a\n                commercial house in this<lb/> country, he would <sic>taken</sic> care of two\n                copies<lb/> to be <sic>writed</sic> by an able sopher.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I hope you will agree in this, in<lb/> every way you will be so kind\n                to answer<lb/> me thereabout in time.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">As for the <hi rend=\"underline\">liste</hi> of Nr.\n                publi-<lb/>cations, I am in the way to form that<lb/> for you, and I will transmit\n                it to you<lb/> very soon <hi rend=\"underline\">via</hi>\n                <placeName>London</placeName> with an exemplar<lb/> of the Nr. Yearbook for\n                    <date>1858</date>, wherein<lb/> you will find, I hope, some interesting<lb/>\n                papers, viz a description of the <placeName>Chazaz</placeName><lb/> kingdom, by\n                    <persName>Mr. Hartog</persName>, a distinguished</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3pr7nk98/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
