                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p><sic>scolar</sic> at <placeName>Leyden</placeName>; an Episode of the<lb/>\n                <sic>mediaval</sic> history of the Jew'<sic>s</sic> in\n                    <placeName>Belgium</placeName>,<lb/> by <persName>Mr. van Lier</persName>; a\n                Jewish novelle,<lb/> by <persName>Mr. van Gigck</persName>, a young lawyer here<lb/>\n                and distinguished <sic>litterat</sic> also. Those<lb/> three original productions\n                may be interes-<lb/>ting to be translated by <persName>Mr. Perez</persName>,\n                for<lb/> the <hi rend=\"underline\">Occident</hi>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Amongst the other works published<lb/> here in the last 25 or 30\n                years for the<lb/> special use of <add>?</add>, there will be<lb/> likewise some\n                that will interest<lb/> you, and I will venture to read<lb/> you as many as\n                possible. I will<lb/> put an advertisement in the only<lb/> Jewish paper we have to\n                promote<lb/> your design.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Will agree, sir, my<lb/> thanks for the informations relating<lb/>\n                to my family and will be so good<lb/> to continue me your correspondence.<lb/> How\n                the <persName>Ancona's</persName> doing now?<lb/> Their last tidings are from\n                    <date>May</date>, I<lb/> believe. I hope they are in good<lb/> health and they\n                have not suffered<lb/> by the financial crisis that has visited<lb/> your shores,\n                like ours.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">Truly yours</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">J. J. Belinfante</persName>\n            </p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3pr7nk98/canvas/p2"
                }
